x4freetext: Ge(Li) detectors 38 and 50 cm2 in volume with an
energy resolution of 2.5 keV for Egamma ~ 1.3 MeV.
Two same targets were irradiated. First target
was irradiated 10 minutes at density beam is
1.08 x 10**12 p/cm2/sec. Another target was irradiated
1 hour at density beam 1.13x 10**12 p/cm2/sec
First measurement has been executed after
50 minutes after irradiation. Each target was measured
65 times during to 5 months after irradiations
This is weighted average for two independent
experiments.
The Error in the calibration of spectrometer.
